					Full Description



		MTI Computers & Software Services Ltd. (MTI) is an Israeli-based telecommunication services company. The Company is active in the development and supply of miniature wireless devices and other products such as lighter-than-air platforms for intelligence use, through its holdings. MTI Wireless Edge Ltd. develops and delivers industry-unique, flat panel antennas for commercial applications, fixed wireless, WiMAX and radio frequency identification readers as well as military antenna solutions spanning the entire radio frequency range (2MHz-40GHz). MTI Engineering Ltd. is a consulting and representation organization that offers a wide range of microwave, telecom and datacom solutions from over 50 companies worldwide. MTeye Security Ltd. designs, develops and markets wireless video surveillance solutions for the cellular telecommunications, security and homeland security and surveillance industries worldwide.
» Full Overview of MTCO.TA







