 Co – CEO and System Eng. : Mr. Menashe ManiMTI Wireless Edge President: Mr. Dov Feiner
Main Business Areas:1. System Engineering Division:
* Concept definition, Technical management and Integration of advanced communication systems.
* Ligter Than Air (LTA) platforms such as Aerostats and Airships. 
* RF and communication subsystems development including short range (ZigBee & BlueTooth) 
2. Wireless Edge (antennas) Ltd.: * Design and manufacture of: 
* All types of antennas in the H.F. through M.M.bands 
* Waveguides
* Flat panel antennas for Fixed Wireless and RFID. 
3. MTeye Security Ltd.* Wireless Video Alarm Subsystems.
Turnover: US$ 16 Million Year: 2005Employees: 95 Year: 2005 Engineers & Technicians: 50 Year: 2005
Special Details:MTI Computers is traded in Tel Aviv stock exchange, Israel.
MTI Wireless Edge is traded in AIM, London, UKWebsite: www.mti-group.co.il
Israel : 11, Hamelacha St. Afek Industrial Park, Rosh Ha'ayin 48101Phone: 972-3-9025050Fax: 972-3-9025051menashe_m@mti-group.co.il
 
 
 
 
 





