Profile data is unavailable for this security.About the companyMTI Computers & Software Services Ltd. (MTI) is an Israeli-based telecommunication services company. The Company is active in the development and supply of miniature wireless devices and other products such as lighter-than-air platforms for intelligence use, through its holdings. MTI Wireless Edge Ltd. develops and delivers industry-unique, flat panel antennas for commercial applications, fixed wireless, WiMAX and radio frequency identification readers as well as military antenna solutions spanning the entire radio frequency range (2MHz-40GHz). MTI Engineering Ltd. is a consulting and representation organization that offers a wide range of microwave, telecom and datacom solutions from over 50 companies worldwide. MTeye Security Ltd. designs, develops and markets wireless video surveillance solutions for the cellular telecommunications, security and homeland security and surveillance industries worldwide. Revenue in ILS (TTM)114.18mNet income in ILS4.62mIncorporated1982Employees80.00LocationMTI Computers & Software Services 1982 Ltd11 Hamelacha st., Afek Industrial ParkROSH HA'AYIN 48091IsraelISRPhone+972  39008900Fax+972  39008901Websitehttp://www.mti-group.com/More ▼Peer analysisKey InformationKey InformationStock PerformancePer Share DataEfficiencyManagement EffectivenessProfitabilityFinancial StrengthGrowth RatesCompanyRevenue (TTM)Net income (TTM)Market capEmployeesPrice/earnings (TTM)Price/book value (MRQ)Price/cash flow (TTM)Price/sales (TTM)EPS (excl. extraordinary items, TTM)EPS (incl. extraordinary items, TTM)Revenue per share (TTM)Book value per share (MRQ)Asset turnover (TTM)Inventory turnover (TTM)Receivables turnover (TTM)Revenues per employee (TTM)Return on avg assets (TTM)Return on avg assets (5 yr avg)Return on investment (TTM)Return on investment (5 yr avg)Gross margin (TTM)Gross margin(5 yr avg)Net profit margin (TTM)Net Profit margin(5 yr avg)Quick ratio (MRQ)Interest coverage (TTM)Tot